<F P=102>  EA0101195594 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in English to 
Rwanda 1900 GMT 1 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA0101195594 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The broad-based transitional (?administration) in 
Rwanda, which was expected to be [word indistinct] today may be 
postponed indefinitely, for President Habyarimana has refused to 
be sworn-in today. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

