<F P=100> EAST AFRICA </F>
<F P=101> Somalia </F>
<H3> <TI>   More German Security Personnel Deployed at Base </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3112202493 Hamburg ARD Television Network in German 1900 
GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD3112202493 </F>
<F P=104>  Hamburg ARD Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Bundeswehr has deployed an additional 33 
security staff at the German base in Belet Uen, Somalia. 
According to the Defense Ministry, they are to reinforce the 
unit for its forthcoming withdrawal. Their deployment is not 
connected with the attack on a German military vehicle in 
Mogadishu on Wednesday. The security personnel were sent to 
Somalia as early as on 20 December. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

