<H3> <TI>   UNITA, Government Clashes, Activities Wrapped Up </TI></H3>
<H4>   Government Attacked in Malanje </H4>
<F P=102> MB3012202993 Luanda Radio Nacional Network in Portuguese 
1900 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>

