<H3> <TI>   Buthelezi Defends kwaZulu Jet Purchase </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0301181794 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 1600 
GMT 3 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0301181794 </F>
