Huambo on 3 January] 
  [Text] [Words indistinct] General Staff of the National 
Union for the Total Independence of Angola [UNITA] Armed Forces 
categorically denies having launched an attack on Malongo in 
Cabinda. 
  2. If the Front for the Liberation of the Cabinda Enclave 
leadership does not claim responsibility for the attack, once 
