<H3> <TI>   Military Seized 1,691 Firearms in Natal in 1993 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0501135794 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1100 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0501135794 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Members of the South African Defense Force [SADF] 
say they have confiscated 1,691 firearms, among them 134 AK-47 
rifles, in Natal last year. Working either alone or with the 
police, they also seized over 1,000 homemade fire arms, hundreds 
of pistols and rifles, 78 grenades, and 27 explosive devices. 

</TEXT>

