Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] We have just heard that alleged UNITA members 
attacked the city of Malanje this morning, which prevented a 
plane carrying three US congressmen from landing. The plane 
turned back to Luanda. This report comes to us from the LUSA 
news agency [Portuguese]. According to Angolan national radio, 
the city of Malanje has been under an intense attack by UNITA 
since the early hours of the morning. A woman was killed in the 
Ritondo district, 2 km from the center of the city, and 3 km 
from the airport. 

