<H4>   Citizens Urged To Expose Assailants </H4>
<F P=102> AB0601204594 Lome Radio Lome in French 1900 GMT 6 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> AB0601204594 </F>
<F P=104>  Lome Radio Lome </F>


