<H4>   Border Attack `Vehemently' Protested </H4>
<F P=102> AB0701083994 Lome Radio Lome in French 0600 GMT 7 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> AB0701083994 </F>
<F P=104>  Lome Radio Lome </F>


