Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Government of Togo has vehemently protested to 
the charge d'affaires of the Ghanaian Embassy in Lome. Armed 
elements from Ghana last night shot at Togolese security agents 
on duty at the main border crossing at Aflao. 

