cooperation is to strengthen the MPLA's military capacity to 
destroy the National Union for the Total Independence of Angola 
(?militarily). This is something Luanda has long sought. It is 
important to note that [words indistinct] FAPLA marines recently 
concluded their military training in Portugal. 

