<H3> <TI>   Update on Government, Renamo Troop Confinement Figures </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0601184694 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1730 GMT 6 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0601184694 </F>
