Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Government soldiers confined to the Namialo 
assembly area in Nampula Province are demanding to know their 
future -- namely, whether they are to be demobilized or to join 
the future apolitical unified army. The 941 soldiers at Namialo 
confinement center want their situations defined so that they 
can start organizing their lives after many years of military 
life. [passage omitted] 

