Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Angolan UNITA [National Union for the Total 
Independence of Angola] rebel group has allegedly bayonetted to 
death 170 civilians in the northern district of Calulo. A local 
government official says the killings took place over the past 
two weeks. Those killed were apparently accused of being 
