<F P=100> REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA </F>
<H3> <TI>   ANC, PAC to Register as Parties Before Election </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB0801123894 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 0500 
GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0801123894 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The ANC [African National Congress] and the PAC 
[Pan-Africanist Congress] have said that they will register as 
political parties before the 27 April election. They announced 
this yesterday in response to reports that they were not going 
to register, because they wanted to take part in the election as 
liberation movements. 

</TEXT>

